2. 源数据清洗并合并¶

发现12年和14年数据的location属性的数据格式为dict数据类型，并且可能包含经纬度，所以从中提取和其他文件相同的值填充，即"address": 的值¶

In [8]:
def extractAddress (x) :
    x = str(x)
    resGroup = re.search(r'address": "(.*?)"',x)
    if resGroup !=None:
        x = resGroup.group().replace('"',"").replace("address: ","")
    else:
        x = None
    return(x)
# address Location 1 
Crime12DF['Location 1'] = Crime12DF['Location 1'].apply(extractAddress)
Crime14DF['Location 1'] = Crime14DF['Location 1'].apply(extractAddress)

In [53]:
# 
descrip = ''
incidentDict={}
for row in itdNull.itertuples(): 
    if incidentDict.get(row[1])!=None:
        descrip = incidentDict[row[1]]
        if descrip !='':
             CrimeDF[row[0]:row[0]+1]['incidentTypeDescription']= descrip
    else:
        simTuple = CrimeDF[(CrimeDF.incidentTypeId==row[1]) & ~(CrimeDF.incidentTypeDescription.isnull())]['incidentTypeDescription']
        if len(simTuple)!=0:
            descrip = simTuple.value_counts().keys()[0]
            incidentDict[row[1]]= descrip
            CrimeDF[row[0]:row[0]+1]['incidentTypeDescription']= descrip

closedTime = CrimeDF[ CrimeDF.closedTime.isnull()][['incidentTypeId','createTime']]
for row in closedTime.itertuples(): 
        x= CrimeDF[(CrimeDF.incidentTypeId==row[1])]['handingTime'].mean()
        CrimeDF[row[0]:row[0]+1]['closedTime']= (CrimeDF[0:1]['createTime']+timedelta(seconds=x)).values[0]
In [64]:
CrimeDF[ CrimeDF.closedTime.isnull()]
Out[64]:
